<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.6.2">
<l>kōvāṉār maṭiyak kolaiyārmaḻuk koṇṭaruḷum</l>
<l>mūvāvā ṉavaṉai muḻunīrvaṇṇa ṉaiyaṭiyārk</l>
<l>kāvāveṉ ṟiraṅkitteṉ ṉaḻuntaiyil maṉṉiniṉṟa</l>
<l>tēvā titēvaṉaiyāṉ kaṇṭukoṇṭuti ḷaittēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having seen for myself the ageless celestial who graciously bore</l>
<l rend="indent">a murderous axe</l>
<l>So that those who were kings died, the one the hue of the vast sea,</l>
<l>Being compassionate to devotees, sighing, “Ah, ah,”</l>
<l rend="indent">the primordial god of gods</l>
<l>Who eternally stands in Aḻuntai of the south, I rejoiced.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
